        "subject": "LU-16035 kfilnd: Handle transaction bad states",
        "message": "LU-16035 kfilnd: Handle transaction bad states\n\nWhen a transaction is transitioned to an unknown state or a invalid\ntransaction event occurs, the transaction is in an unrecoverable\nstate. This should only occur if kfilnd has a bug. Thus, treat\ntransactions in an unrecoverable state as an LBUG().\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial\nHPE-bug-id: LUS-9379\nSigned-off-by: Ian Ziemba <ian.ziemba@hpe.com>\nChange-Id: Id69d8a98d58fd926154ad32fa6689d5d5880541a\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
